Simply ask Alexa to turn on/off, change the speed settings, night mode and be able to turn on/off the device. 
Connect Alexa to your Bionaire app in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our "Bionaire" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register a Bionaire account in our "Bionaire" app;
(3). You need to have Bionaire device on hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Bionaire" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Bionaire" skills; 
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market; 
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app; 
(7). Search "Bionaire" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Bionaire", and you'll be navigated to Bionaire login page;
(9).Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking; 
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your Bionaire air purifier like these: 
“Alexa, turn on air purifier" 
“Alexa, turn off air purifier" 
“Alexa, set air purifier fan speed to high/low/mid"
